sequenceDiagram
actor User
participant WebServer
participant API
participant Database2
participant FileStorage
participant EmailService
participant Authentication
participant LoginPage
participant Dashboard

User->>WebServer: Access Website
WebServer->>User: Serves UI
User->>LoginPage: Logs In
LoginPage->>Authentication: Validates Credentials
Authentication->>API: Auth Token
API->>Database: User Data
Database-->>API: User Data
API-->>Authentication: Auth Response
Authentication-->>LoginPage: Login Success
LoginPage-->>User: Redirect to Dashboard
User->>Dashboard: View Tasks
Dashboard->>API: Get Tasks
API->>Database: Task Data
Database-->>API: Task Data
API-->>Dashboard: Task List
Dashboard-->>User: Display Tasks
User->>Dashboard: Create Task
Dashboard->>API: Create Task
API->>Database: Create Task
Database-->>API: Task Created
API-->>Dashboard: Task Created
Dashboard-->>User: Task Created
User->>Dashboard: Update Task
Dashboard->>API: Update Task
API->>Database: Update Task
Database-->>API: Task Updated
API-->>Dashboard: Task Updated
Dashboard-->>User: Task Updated
User->>Dashboard: Delete Task
Dashboard->>API: Delete Task
API->>Database: Delete Task
Database-->>API: Task Deleted
API-->>Dashboard: Task Deleted
Dashboard-->>User: Task Deleted
User->>Dashboard: Upload File
Dashboard->>API: Upload File
API->>FileStorage: Upload File
FileStorage-->>API: File Uploaded
API-->>Dashboard: File Uploaded
Dashboard-->>User: File Uploaded
User->>Dashboard: Send Notification
Dashboard->>API: Send Notification
API->>EmailService: Send Email
EmailService-->>API: Email Sent
API-->>Dashboard: Notification Sent
Dashboard-->>User: Notification Sent